data.description: Discover country living in the city! This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom brick home, in the sought-after Jack Britt High School district, boasts a NEW ROOF & WINDOWS, luxury vinyl plank floors, new front door and screen/storm door, updated vanities, and ample natural light in the open, spacious living area.  Situated on a .43-acre fenced-in lot with apple & persimmon trees, a shed, and backing onto a lake and woods on two sides. Enjoy the convenience of city living with top-tier schools and come home to the peace of the countryside. Schedule your showing today!
